trans-unit.source: Stores <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Enregistre les objets <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection> class is used by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage> to provide a list of the input languages installed on the system.
trans-unit.target: Le <xref:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection> classe est utilisée par <xref:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage> pour fournir une liste des langues d’entrée installées sur le système.

trans-unit.source: You cannot directly create an instance of this class.
trans-unit.target: Vous ne pouvez pas créer directement une instance de cette classe.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> to locate.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> à rechercher.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" /> contains the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtient une valeur indiquant si <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" /> contient le <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> spécifié.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> is contained in the collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> est contenu dans la collection ; sinon <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional array that is the destination of the values copied from <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Tableau unidimensionnel qui constitue la destination des valeurs copiées à partir de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The index in <c>array</c> where copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Index dans le <c>tableau</c> à partir duquel la copie commence.

trans-unit.source: Copies the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" /> values to a one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Copie les valeurs de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" /> vers une instance de <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensionnelle, à l'index spécifié.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> specifies a multidimensional array.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> spécifie un tableau multidimensionnel.

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: - ou -

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" /> is greater than the available space between the <paramref name="index" /> and the end of <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: Le nombre d'éléments dans <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" /> est supérieur à la quantité d'espace disponible entre <paramref name="index" /> et la fin de <paramref name="array" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> est <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than the lower bound of <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> est inférieur à la limite inférieure d’<paramref name="array" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> to locate.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> à rechercher.

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Retourne l'index de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> dans <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The index of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" />, if found; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: Index de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> dans <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" />, s'il existe ; sinon, -1.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the entry to locate in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Index de base zéro de l’entrée à rechercher dans la collection.

trans-unit.source: Gets the entry at the specified index of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtient l'entrée à l'index spécifié du <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguageCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> at the specified index of the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.InputLanguage" /> dans l'index spécifié de la collection.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is outside the valid range of indexes for the collection.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> est en dehors de la plage valide des index pour la collection.
